# A Complete Beginner's Guide to Next.js

I've used [Create React App](https://reactjs.org/docs/create-a-new-react-app.html) non-stop to scaffold React apps, and I **love** it. Recently, though, I've been using Next.js for more and more of them. It has a bunch of great features like routing and server-side rendering that offer amazing experiences for both end-users and developers.

